Abezimo eziphuthumayo babizelwe esigamekweni sokudubula ebhulohweni lika-N2 kuHigginson Highway namuhla emini. Okhulumela abe-ALS Paramedics uGarrith Jamieson uthi bafike endaweni yesigameko bathola kunabantu abanamanxeba okudutshulwa. Bane abantu abahlolwe kwabonakala ukuthi bashonile, kusinde oyedwa, osegaxwe ozankosi. Kusolakala ukuthi abasolwa bebejahwa amaphoyisa ngemuva kokuzama ukuduna imoto eMusgrave, eThekwini. UMgwaqo u-N2 usavaliwe njengoba amaphoyisa asahlola indawo yesigameko. Police shot 5 people dead in Higginson High way in Durban mid day today pic.twitter.com/xV9ciHLvIF UDABA OLUPHELELE EPHEPHENI LAKHO LAKUSASA 